<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77ad3e7f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s459c–6a"><num value="459c–6a">§ 459c–6a.</num><heading> The Clem Miller Environmental Education Center; designation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall designate the principal environmental education center within the seashore as “The Clem Miller Environmental Education Center”, in commemoration of the vision and leadership which the late Representative Clem Miller gave to the creation and protection of Point Reyes National Seashore.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77ad3e80-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/87/657/s7">Pub. L. 87–657, § 7</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/94/544/s4/b">Pub. L. 94–544, § 4(b)</ref>, <date date="1976-10-18">Oct. 18, 1976</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/90/2515">90 Stat. 2515</ref>, and <ref href="/us/pl/94/567/s7/b">Pub. L. 94–567, § 7(b)</ref>, <date date="1976-10-20">Oct. 20, 1976</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/90/2695">90 Stat. 2695</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
